1.Type in the city name and choose hotel, click Search button, it will show the relative hotels list
2. Click the the hotel shown on the hotelist,it will pop up an window, allow the facebook post
3.When type in wrong city name, it will show an error message
4.When type in nothing, but click search button, it will show an message to let you type in city name
5. Some of the code come from the internet, here are their links:
post to Facebook:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/5170355/android-send-a-facebook-post-with-custom-actions
listview:
http://www.eoeandroid.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=155265
